testing requirements at entry at the borders, for shopping, visiting family and friends and in similar situations.|However, basic obligations such as the mask mandate in public spaces or keeping distance/avoiding crowds will not be lifted for an extended period of time, and, most importantly:\n\"Auch ein Anspruch auf die Öffnung bestimmter Einrichtungen - etwa Museen oder Schwimmbäder - ergibt sich nach Einschätzung der Bundesregierung aus den für Geimpfte und Genesene festzulegenden Ausnahmen nicht.\"\n(The federal government assesses the legal situation that from these exemptions there is no obligation or legal alley derived for those fully vaccinated or those recovered from COVID-19 to demand that institutions such as museums, water parks, amusement parks or similar open particularly for them.)\nhttps://www.berlin.de/aktuelles/berlin/6528127-958092-bund-und-laender-beraten-ueber-lockerung.html','https://www.gjopen.com/comments/1268890','Upvote\n    (1)',NULL),(809,4,'bobrown','2021-04-24 21:09:00',5,'Given the recent legislation to permit the federal government to issue regulations based on infection rates, and the introduction of restrictions due to current conditions, I am lowering my forecast by half. Vaccinations are continuing a pace at a rate of about 500K/day which is good but not great. The vaccine supply is about to dramatically increase in the EU, it depends on how quickly the medical system can pivot to increase the daily rate. If the vaccination rate can be increased by 50% in May, then the chances of opening to the public may improve.','https://www.gjopen.com/comments/1268353','Upvote\n    (0)',NULL),(811,4,'here_to_learn','2021-04-23 09:11:00',20,'It\'s stated that the collection for asian art will open in autumn. Since the vaccination is slowly progressing and infection and death rates are still rising. \nI would state that the probability is a low.','https://www.gjopen.com/comments/1267612','Upvote\n    (0)',NULL),(812,4,'Deanrock','2021-04-22 14:16:00',95,'all lockdowns are subject to citizen fatigue, and this year more than ever. by summer lockdowns will be finished','https://www.gjopen.com/comments/1267111','Upvote\n    (0)',NULL),(813,4,'SE_Meyer','2021-04-21 11:49:00',5,'The German parliament is currently discussing the federal emergency brake mechanism (\"Bundesnotbremse\") and will likely vote to accept it later today against the votes of AfD, Die Linke MP\'s.\nThe current version of the law, which has been fast-tracked amid a surge of infections in April, currently contains no exception for people fully vaccinate with respect to applicability. However, for certain situations being fully vaccinated may lead to an exemption from testing obligations.|A court recently dismissed a law suit of two fully vaccinated individuals against the rules of the city of Gießen (Hessia), which among others contain curfews at night. The court decision, which could be a landmark case in this respect, said that there is too little scientific evidence of \"sterilizing immunity\" (inability to infect others) achieved through full vaccination, so that all rules still do apply for these two individuals, despite being fully vaccinated.\nThis makes it harder for publicly owned museums to have preferred entry for the vaccinated, or any other concepts that eases hygiene measures in public spaces.\nMuseums could be forced to remain closed until the status of assumed herd immunity in Germany and/or Berlin will be achieved, as a consequence.','https://www.gjopen.com/comments/1266658','Upvote\n    (0)',NULL),(814,4,'2021_cp','2021-04-20 16:04:00',50,'Berlin is again in lockdown, the vaccination rhythm is slow','https://www.gjopen.com/comments/1266279','Upvote\n    (0)',NULL),(815,4,'zzzauberfuchs','2021-04-19 15:34:00',99,'By AUG 1 already a lot og peple will be vacinated, plus tests are available thus i am sure that within July, there will be the possibility to visit,  at least with test and or vaccinated visitors will be possible.'